## Your Positioning

<!-- How you're positioned in the market. If you've run /positioning-audit,
     paste the summary here. -->

```
Category:               [What market do you play in?]
For:                    [Who is it for — specific persona]
Who need:               [What job they hire you for]
Unlike:                 [The competitive alternative — what they'd do without you]
We:                     [Your key differentiator — the one thing you win on]
```

### Positioning Landmines

<!-- Things you should NEVER claim or imply in messaging. -->

- [e.g., "Never say 'all-in-one' — we're not, and it invites comparison to platforms we can't match"]
- [e.g., "Never claim enterprise-grade security — we don't have SOC 2 yet"]
- [e.g., "Avoid '10x faster' — legal flagged this, use 'significantly faster' or cite specific benchmarks"]

